title: Xamarin 4.6.6 (Studio, Android, iOS)
description:
INSTRUCTIONS

 1. unzip 7-zip format.
 2. Istall the Xamarin Installer 2.0.
 3. Run MFx Patcher.
 4. Click Patch.

 ENJOY! If you like the software, Buy more cracks from me ;) 


 PREREQUISITES & NOTES

 - This patch only supports: [Xamarin.Android 4.6.06000], [Xamarin.iOS 1.0.897] and [Xamarin Studio 4.0.8]
 - You need Visual Studio Professional (2010/2012) or better to use the extensions from Xamarin.
 - The patch will not work if there's installed another version of a supported product.
 - The patch is reversible, just use the unpatch button.


 INDEPENDENT INSTALLERS

 Install in the following order:(Included)

 1. JDK 6 
 2. Android SDK 
 3. Android NDK
 4. GTK# 
 5. Xamarin.Android
 6. Xamarin.iOS
 7. Xamarin Studio

 Having troubles and going to ask? Give also information about installed products, versions installed, and the complete output text that the patcher gives.
